{"tid":543392,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州攝度5度下街訪 街上年青人不懂粵語令人心寒","createTime":"2018-01-28T12:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T00:21:49.000Z","uid":122054,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"240c0dd5addb5c871141acaaa903919305932677","tid":543392,"uid":122054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:32:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/junkbay/permalink/2093290344281106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fjunkbay%2Fpermalink%2F2093290344281106&d=5DDn6lKicMIujhLNYaocQ9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=da6f6c35\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/junkbay/permalink/2093290344281106</a><br />\n<br />\n片中在街上，三位受訪高三(即中六、99/00年出生)學生已在日常生活中<br />\n只用普通話交談，原來佢地呢代，幼稚園已經要學普通話，所以受訪既<br />\n幾個簡單粵語詞語都講唔出了，佢地亦異口同聲說日常生活極少說粵語<br />\n，但明白身為廣州人不懂粵語的現象很不正常。<br />\n<br />\n之所以拍呢條片，做呢個訪問，係因為佢地上幾個禮拜訪問左D老一輩<br />\n，佢地紛紛表示不擔心將來粵語會被消滅既可能性。<br />\n<br />\n然而，我地可見到可笑同心寒既係，<br />\n滅粵風暴，已經殺到去20歲以下呢一輩，<br />\n再係咁落去，不出20年就可以達到黨既目標 - 消滅粵語。"},{"pid":"104f1f696020a436d0f129b043b79ea8f3655cbb","tid":543392,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"so what連登開始關心中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ed73176bcf3f381b9489548ef941f3fc56385d","tid":543392,"uid":73310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"104f1f696020a436d0f129b043b79ea8f3655cbb","tid":543392,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"so what連登開始關心中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T15:54:34.000Z","msg":"係我地香港都面對緊同樣問題啊<img src=\"/as